Class SavannahBiomTree

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.trees.BiomTree
de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.trees.SavannahBiomTree
public class SavannahBiomTree
extends BiomTree
This class is a subclass of BiomTree. It creates a standard tree for the Savannah. This class will also only be created in the Savannah Biom.
